            </div>
            <div class="text-xs text-on-surface-variant mt-2 leading-relaxed flex flex-col gap-1">
                <p>Summer Is Volley & A.S.D. Iuno. Tutti i diritti riservati.</p>
                <VDB />
                &copy; 2025 - {year}
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</footer>
